currentQuizSentences: [{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-15","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-15","句子":"The company absorbed the smaller startup into its operations","中文":"（公司將這家較小的新創企業納入其運營中。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-18","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-18","句子":"The car's suspension system absorbs the bumps in the road to provide a smoother ride","中文":"（汽車的懸掛系統吸收路面的顛簸，以提供更平穩的行駛。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorption-1","分類":"Design","Words":"absorption-1","名人":"Leonardo da Vinci","句子":"To truly master a skill, one must engage in deep absorption, losing oneself in the process of learning.","中文":"要真正掌握一項技能，必須全神貫注地投入學習過程，忘卻自我。"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorption-5","分類":"Design","Words":"absorption-5","句子":"The plant's roots are responsible for the absorption of nutrients from the soil","中文":"（植物的根負責從土壤中吸收養分。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-14","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-14","句子":"The children absorbed the lesson quickly and were eager to try it themselves","中文":"（孩子們迅速吸收了這節課的內容，並渴望親自嘗試。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorption-4","分類":"Design","Words":"absorption-4","句子":"The sponge's absorption of water was rapid","中文":"（海綿對水的吸收速度很快。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-4","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-4","名人":"Steve Jobs","句子":"Your mind is like a sponge—be careful what you absorb, because it shapes what you create.","中文":"（你的思維就像海綿——小心你吸收的東西，因為它決定了你創造的事物。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-16","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-16","句子":"He absorbed the new culture after living abroad for several years","中文":"（他在國外生活多年後融入了新文化。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-10","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-10","句子":"The towel absorbed the spilled water quickly","中文":"（毛巾迅速吸收了灑出的水。）"},{"音檔":"音檔 - absorb-2","分類":"Design","Words":"absorb-2","名人":"Barack Obama","句子":"In a divided world, we must absorb the differences and turn them into understanding.","中文":"（在分裂的世界裡，我們必須吸收彼此的不同，並將其轉化為理解。）"}]
